SUMMARY:Sniper Elite V2 Remastered | Ep. 5 - St. Olibartus Church
DESCRIPTION:The stealth and precision continue in Sniper Elite V2
 Remastered. Careful positioning, patience, and those signature slow-motion
 moments. In the dark days of the end of World War 2 amidst the ruins of
 Berlin, one bullet can change history... Elite sniper Karl Fairburne
 returns to the front line in the remaster of this award-winning
 stealth-action experience. Packed with new features, contemporary visuals
 and definitive content.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=25XEsqm1F6k
CATEGORIES:Sniper Elite V2 Remastered
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:stream-22732211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260226T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260324T231900Z
DTSTART:20260319T213000Z
DTEND:20260319T233000Z
SUMMARY:Retro Rewind - Video Store Simulator | Ep. 1 - Be Kind, Rewind...
 Or Face Judgment
DESCRIPTION:A brand-new retro-inspired adventure begins in Video Store
 Simulator! Stock the shelves, manage the chaos, and relive the glory days
 of VHS... or suffer the consequences. Manage your very own video store in
 the early 90s! Rent, sell, decorate and expand your business from the
 ground up and relive the golden ages of video rentals!
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r5jQeFAnKLs
CATEGORIES:Retro Rewind - Video Store Simulator
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:stream-22752211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260228T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260324T231900Z
DTSTART:20260321T213000Z
DTEND:20260321T233000Z
SUMMARY:Fallout 4 | Ep. 41 - Theme Park Safety Standards = Zero
DESCRIPTION:Back to the chaos of Fallout 4. Nuka-World remains exactly as
 safe as you'd expect - which is to say, not at all. As the sole survivor
 of Vault 111, you enter a world destroyed by nuclear war. Every second is
 a fight for survival, and every choice is yours. Only you can rebuild and
 determine the fate of the Wasteland. Welcome home.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JrujtDSS4EQ
CATEGORIES:Fallout 4
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
