SUMMARY:Sniper Elite V2 Remastered | Ep. 6 - Tiergarten Flak Tower
DESCRIPTION:Precision and patience are key as we continue our sniper
 campaign. One shot, one opportunity... and hopefully not one mistake too
 many. In the dark days of the end of World War 2 amidst the ruins of
 Berlin, one bullet can change history... Elite sniper Karl Fairburne
 returns to the front line in the remaster of this award-winning
 stealth-action experience. Packed with new features, contemporary visuals
 and definitive content.
